- **Button** (`/components/BoxedInputFields/Button.js`): Customizable button component with different styles.
- **CheckboxField** (`/components/BoxedInputFields/CheckboxField.js`): Checkbox input with label.
- **DateField** (`/components/BoxedInputFields/DateField.js`): Date picker field.
